# Once done this will define
#
#  LIBETONYEK_FOUND       - LibEtonyek is available
#  LIBETONYEK_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directory, e.g. /usr/include
#  LIBETONYEK_LIBRARIES   - the libraries needed to use LibEtonyek
